NITORIZAR Na+","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"Hipopotasemia → suplementar K+","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"257","text":"Hipotension ortostatica → riesgo caidas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"257","text":"Hiperuricemia → gota","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"262","parent":"0","text":"PROFILAXIS MIGRAÑA VESTIBULAR","guid":"","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"VERAPAMILO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"Farmacodinamica → bloqueador Ca2+ tipo L","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"263","text":"Dosis → 80-120mg c/12h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"263","text":"GERIATRIA → riesgo bradicardia, constipacion, hipotension","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"267","parent":"262","text":"AMITRIPTILINA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"268","parent":"267","text":"Farmacodinamica → antidepresivo triciclico, modulacion serotoninergica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"267","text":"Dosis → 10-25mg nocturna (inicio bajo en AM)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"267","text":"GERIATRIA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"271","parent":"270","text":"ALTA carga anticolinergica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"270","text":"Riesgo caidas, delirium, arritmias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"270","text":"Alternativa → nortriptilina (menor efecto anticolinergico)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"274","parent":"262","text":"TOPIRAMATO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"275","parent":"274","text":"Dosis → 25-50mg c/12h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"274","text":"GERIATRIA → riesgo cognitivo, nefrolitiasis, acidosis metabolica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"277","parent":"262","text":"PROPRANOLOL","guid":"","children":[{"id":"278","parent":"277","text":"Dosis → 20-40mg c/12h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"277","text":"GERIATRIA → bradicardia, broncoespasmo, depresion, enmascaramiento hipoglicemia","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"280","parent":"0","text":"REHABILITACION VESTIBULAR","guid":"","children":[{"id":"281","parent":"280","text":"NO ES FARMACO pero es PRIMERA LINEA en AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"280","text":"Compensacion central depende de NO usar supresores cronicamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"280","text":"Ejercicios de habituacion, estabilizacion de mirada, equilibrio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"280","text":"Evidencia nivel 1A en vertigo periferico cronico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"280","text":"En AM → reduce riesgo caidas 30-50%","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"286","parent":"0","text":"ALGORITMO GERIATRICO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"287","parent":"286","text":"Crisis aguda (<72h)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"288","parent":"287","text":"1ra linea → betahistina 16mg c/8h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"287","text":"Si vomitos → ondansetron 4mg IV/SL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"287","text":"Si nausea intensa → domperidona 10mg (con ECG previo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"287","text":"EVITAR → dimenhidrinato, BZD, escopolamina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"287","text":"Si imprescindible supresor → lorazepam 0.5mg x1 dosis (excepcional)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"293","parent":"286","text":"Meniere","guid":"","children":[{"id":"294","parent":"293","text":"Betahistina 48mg/dia → minimo 3 meses","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"295","parent":"293","text":"Dieta hiposodica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"293","text":"HCTZ 25mg/dia → con control Na+ y K+","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"297","parent":"286","text":"Migraña vestibular profilaxis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"298","parent":"297","text":"1ra linea AM → verapamilo 80mg c/12h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"297","text":"2da linea → nortriptilina 10-25mg noche","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"297","text":"EVITAR flunarizina si posible en AM","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"301","parent":"286","text":"Neuritis vestibular","guid":"","children":[{"id":"302","parent":"301","text":"Metilprednisolona ciclo corto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"301","text":"Betahistina + rehabilitacion vestibular precoz","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"304","parent":"301","text":"Supresor maximo 48h","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"305","parent":"286","text":"Post-agudo (>72h)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"306","parent":"305","text":"SUSPENDER supresores vestibulares","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"307","parent":"305","text":"Iniciar rehabilitacion vestibular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"308","parent":"305","text":"Betahistina puede continuar (no retrasa compensacion)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"309","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clinicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"310","parent":"309","text":"Betahistina es el UNICO antivertiginoso que NO retrasa compensacion vestibular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"311","parent":"309","text":"Dimenhidrinato tiene carga anticolinergica equivalente a difenhidramina → EVITAR en AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"312","parent":"309","text":"Cinarizina/flunarizina causan parkinsonismo → revisar en TODO paciente AM con extrapiramidalismo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"313","parent":"309","text":"Lorazepam es la BZD de eleccion si imprescindible en AM (glucuronidacion, sin metabolitos activos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"314","parent":"309","text":"Ondansetron es el antiemetico MAS seguro en AM → sin efecto antidopaminergico ni anticolinergico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"315","parent":"309","text":"El sobreuso de supresores vestibulares es causa PREVENIBLE de vertigo cronico en AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"316","parent":"309","text":"En AM con vertigo → SIEMPRE revisar lista de farmacos como causa (hipotensores, BZD, anticolinergicos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"317","parent":"309","text":"Flunarizina T1/2 18 dias → los EA persisten SEMANAS despues de suspender","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"318","parent":"309","text":"Rehabilitacion vestibular reduce caidas 30-50% → es la intervencion mas costo-efectiva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"319","parent":"309","text":"Domperidona → ECG OBLIGATORIO antes de iniciar en AM (QTc)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"320","parent":"0","text":"VER TAMBIEN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"321","parent":"320","text":"→ Vertigo y Sindromes Vestibulares (ORL)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"322","parent":"320","text":"→ Delirium en UCI (Farmacologia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"323","parent":"320","text":"→ Polifarmacia y Deprescripcion (Geriatria)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"324","parent":"320","text":"→ Caidas en el Adulto Mayor (Geriatria)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"325","parent":"320","text":"→ Migraña Vestibular (ORL)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"326","parent":"320","text":"→ Enfermedad de Meniere (ORL)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"327","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"328","parent":"327","text":"1. Hain TC, Uddin M. Pharmacological treatment of vertigo. CNS Drugs. 2003;17(2):85-100.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"329","parent":"327","text":"2. Rascol O, et al. Antivertigo medications and drug-induced vertigo. Drugs. 1995;50(5):777-91.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"330","parent":"327","text":"3. Casani AP, et al. Current Insights into Treating Vertigo in Older Adults. Drugs Aging. 2021;38(8):655-670.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"331","parent":"327","text":"4. Ramos Alcocer R, et al. Use of betahistine in the treatment of peripheral vertigo. Acta Otolaryngol. 2015;135(12):1205-11.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"332","parent":"327","text":"5. Strupp M, et al. Methylprednisolone, valacyclovir, or the combination for vestibular neuritis. N Engl J Med. 2004;351(4):354-61.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"333","parent":"327","text":"6. American Geriatrics Society Beers Criteria Update Expert Panel. AGS Beers Criteria 2023. J Am Geriatr Soc. 2023;71(7):2052-2077.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"334","parent":"327","text":"7. O'Mahony D, et al. STOPP/START criteria v3. Age Ageing. 2023;52(suppl 2):afad042.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":334,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"ORL","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología","filename":"Farmacos Vertigo iPad","id":"map_1561","resolved_references":[]}